{"tid":2408338,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭若驊斥有人或故意誤解《港區國安法》　 法章明文保障人權法治","createTime":"2021-02-14T23:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T06:33:53.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"acbf96de72bb955bbf3ef9741be6b2293cfa4736","tid":2408338,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"律政司長鄭若驊接受本台訪問時，回應有評論指，《港區國安法》實施以來，檢控人數偏低。她解釋，由於檢控門檻高於拘捕門檻，要證明有合理定罪機會，在部分案件，律政司等待警方作進一步蒐證。對於終審法院近日審議一宗《國安法》相關的保釋上訴，沒有海外非常任法官參與，鄭若驊認為有關爭議「有少許借題發揮」，說判斷裁決公正與否，最重要是看法官判詞。 <br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊說《國安法》實施以來，香港社會平穩下來、由亂及治，但有些人故意，或者由於不清晰，而對《國安法》錯誤理解。她說本港法治基礎仍然穩固，作為仲裁及國際法律中心地位不變。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379057&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eUwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=5f0a8312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379057</a>"},{"pid":"8f44baf2551f62e15a359af47b96b60ee13a706c","tid":2408338,"uid":8170,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T23:53:51.000Z","msg":"最錯誤咪佢囉"},{"pid":"acc35d9140cb4102ac5f9d281bdcd01b95fb34de","tid":2408338,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"唔係當場槍斃已經係人權"},{"pid":"5bfabd58e91bbdad3171e1ab606d46c6b20f914a","tid":2408338,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T23:58:33.000Z","msg":"noted"},{"pid":"ce6d1d8a620aa6ccebda246827cd09d1a017a4c8","tid":2408338,"uid":318720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"有人故意誤解一國兩制"},{"pid":"0b908c93494449106428abcfafcfee81f14987df","tid":2408338,"uid":42700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:03:20.000Z","msg":"dklm"},{"pid":"43c1da55c733a897d27c2a8295dd6d7d1c633f93","tid":2408338,"uid":278038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:09:14.000